  <p>
A 
    <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
            keyref="business_definition_clinical_dental_technician">Clinical Dental Technician</xref>
 is a 
    <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_care_professional">CARE PROFESSIONAL</xref>
.  </p>
  <p>
A 
    <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
            keyref="business_definition_clinical_dental_technician">Clinical Dental Technician</xref>
 (
    <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
            keyref="business_definition_clinical_dental_technician">CDT</xref>
) is a registered 
    <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
            keyref="business_definition_dental_care_professional">Dental Care Professional</xref>
 who provides complete dentures directly to 
    <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_patient">PATIENTS</xref>
 and other dental devices on prescription from a dentist  </p>
  <p>
      <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
            keyref="business_definition_clinical_dental_technician">Clinical Dental Technicians</xref>
 are also qualified 
    <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
            keyref="business_definition_dental_technician">Dental Technicians</xref>
.  </p>

